name: Planes: War Flight Sim 2016 Pro
description:
New Level Of War Plane Sim Pro!

Planes: War Flight Sim 2016 - not another sorority app, this is game for true mean man!
Let's check your fatigue! Download now and play! No ads! As cool as San Andreas!
10 different planes and 15 fatigue missions are waiting for you.
Only rockets and gunplay.
Control is simple, lead the laserpointer and than shoot.
Enemies are mean and hard. 3 bosses check your fatigue.
Download Planes: War Flight Sim 2016 Pro and beat the records, pilot!
